---
title: Sesame Honey Popcorn Chicken Stir-Fry with Rapid Rice & Asian Veggies
description: Put down that phone and throw out the takeaway menu because you won’t be needing them anymore! Let’s take juicy chicken
and toss them in a honey-oyster sauce mix then sprinkle sesame seeds all over for a taste of nostalgia. A side of super-speedy
rice is perfect to soak up the extra sauce.

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving.*
